{"tid":2202990,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"美國更新香港旅遊警示  勸籲國民 “三思而後行”","createTime":"2020-09-15T04:39:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-15T08:43:47.000Z","uid":28114,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d465276dee6a3a19c64e4133aace1bef5c235bdc","tid":2202990,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T04:39:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://gdb.voanews.com/AA3143AF-0822-4A5C-A50B-B14125F07CA2_w650_r1_s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgdb.voanews.com%2FAA3143AF-0822-4A5C-A50B-B14125F07CA2_w650_r1_s.jpg&h=17877f1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國更新香港旅遊警示<br />\n<br />\n針對&ldquo;港版國安法&rdquo;在香港實施兩個半月後，美國政府首次勸籲準備前往香港的國民重新考慮行程，避免因曾經公開批評中國，在到達香港後被捕控告。<br />\n<br />\n美國國務院星期一更新針對香港的旅遊警示，除了如常提及新冠疫情因素外，還首次提及&ldquo;港版國安法&rdquo;，將旅遊警戒級別由第二級&ldquo;提高警覺&rdquo;（Exercise increased caution）提升至&ldquo;三思而後行&rdquo;（Reconsider travel）。<br />\n<br />\n美國國務院在官方網站提到，&ldquo;港版國安法&rdquo;自7月1日生效後，中國顯示意圖運用權力針對他們所界定的&ldquo;分裂國家&rdquo;行為、顛覆、恐怖主義與&ldquo;勾結&rdquo;外國勢力等廣泛活動，單方面任意在香港行使警察與治安權。<br />\n<br />\n國務院發出的旅遊警示特別提到，&ldquo;港版國安法&rdquo;涵蓋非香港居民與香港以外機構的罪行，導致公開批評中國的美國公民被捕、驅逐、起訴的風險增加，並指中國國家安全公署已經在香港運作。<br />\n<br />\n這份更新旅遊警示提醒在香港的美國公民，參與香港的示威活動有可能被香港當局解讀為顛覆政權、發動恐怖主義或與外國勢力勾結，從而招致被控刑事罪行。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.voacantonese.com/a/s-dc-rc-us-urges-citizens-to-reconsider-traveling-to-hong-kong/5583771.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voacantonese.com%2Fa%2Fs-dc-rc-us-urges-citizens-to-reconsider-traveling-to-hong-kong%2F5583771.html&d=B6Sv%2FagOPA3DZgijvYhacdMQoCHxbgs64DeXVNsql00%3D&h=df715120\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.voacantonese.com/a/s-dc-rc-us-urges-citizens-to-reconsider-traveling-to-hong-kong/5583771.html</a>"},{"pid":"52569d75c5961697753efe3c2ebe3428f47a0106","tid":2202990,"uid":119864,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T04:41:07.000Z","msg":"又賣地又叫人唔好去，就快開打<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c85f0586532e3388b505458bd24e56b99afd991","tid":2202990,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T04:41:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"128bf3c8e4fa0e6a700eedcc1e3e32c3b13546bc","tid":2202990,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T05:18:09.000Z","msg":"左膠：歧視中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c35f1898d551e0032a9489bb97cf450ffbbea8c","tid":2202990,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T08:16:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=405592\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D405592&d=B6Sv%2FagOPA3DZgijvYhacdMQoCHxbgs64DeXVNsql00%3D&h=4b3753cd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D405592&h=b8ad913f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=405592</a>"},{"pid":"933a4c8c7698e123f8c26fd9b5b505d93aa4fa85","tid":2202990,"uid":254442,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T08:34:07.000Z","msg":"中国幾時反制番 唔俾人去美國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4053047225a03f4d0df8623502553ed74c1af69","tid":2202990,"uid":215755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T08:43:47.000Z","msg":"遲早會有黑警當街擄走美國鬼佬做人質"}]}